.TH "LIGHTNING-INVOICE-EXPIRY-SET" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-invoice-expiry-set \- create an invoice with a custom expiry
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning invoice-expiry-set
.I amount_msat label expiry_seconds
.RI [ desc ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Creates a BOLT11 invoice with a custom expiry time in seconds.
.PP
Output: JSON object from CLN's invoice command including payment_hash, bolt11, expires_at.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-invoice-decode (1),
.BR lightning-invoice-create-offer (1)
